---
/**
 * rest-api/0010 · Figure 2 — the job as a state machine: queued → running, which
 * resolves to exactly one terminal state, succeeded (a result link) or failed
 * (an error). One envelope, four states.
 *
 * Copied VERBATIM from the source HTML (figure + svg + figcaption incl. the
 * footnote <sup>). Lives as an .astro component for the kebab-case-SVG reason.
 * The markers it references (#arw, #arwG, #arwR) come from the source's global
 * hidden <svg>, which does not travel with the figure, so they're inlined here
 * in a local <defs>, fills/ids verbatim.
 */
---

<figure>
    <svg
        viewBox="0 0 600 170"
        role="img"
        aria-label="Job state machine: queued transitions to running, which transitions to either succeeded with a result link, or failed with an error. Succeeded and failed are terminal."
    >
        <defs>
            <marker
                id="arw"
                viewBox="0 0 10 10"
                refX="8.5"
                refY="5"
                markerWidth="7"
                markerHeight="7"
                orient="auto-start-reverse"
                ><path d="M0,0 L10,5 L0,10 z" fill="#6b675f"></path></marker
            >
            <marker
                id="arwG"
                viewBox="0 0 10 10"
                refX="8.5"
                refY="5"
                markerWidth="7"
                markerHeight="7"
                orient="auto-start-reverse"
                ><path d="M0,0 L10,5 L0,10 z" fill="#2f5d3a"></path></marker
            >
            <marker
                id="arwR"
                viewBox="0 0 10 10"
                refX="8.5"
                refY="5"
                markerWidth="7"
                markerHeight="7"
                orient="auto-start-reverse"
                ><path d="M0,0 L10,5 L0,10 z" fill="#9a2417"></path></marker
            >
        </defs>
        <g font-family="ui-sans-serif,system-ui,sans-serif">
            <text
                x="300"
                y="18"
                text-anchor="middle"
                font-size="12"
                font-weight="700"
                fill="#111110">STATUS RESOURCE = A SMALL STATE MACHINE</text
            >
            <rect x="20" y="64" width="120" height="46" rx="9" fill="#fff" stroke="#6b675f"></rect>
            <text x="80" y="84" text-anchor="middle" font-size="12" font-weight="700">queued</text>
            <text x="80" y="100" text-anchor="middle" font-size="8.5" fill="#6b675f"
                >accepted, waiting</text
            >
            <line x1="140" y1="87" x2="194" y2="87" stroke="#6b675f" marker-end="url(#arw)"></line>
            <rect x="196" y="64" width="120" height="46" rx="9" fill="#eef2f5" stroke="#1f3a5a"
            ></rect>
            <text
                x="256"
                y="84"
                text-anchor="middle"
                font-size="12"
                font-weight="700"
                fill="#1f3a5a">running</text
            >
            <text x="256" y="100" text-anchor="middle" font-size="8.5" fill="#6b675f"
                >worker picked it up</text
            >
            <!-- to succeeded -->
            <path
                d="M 316 78 C 360 60, 400 48, 442 48"
                fill="none"
                stroke="#2f5d3a"
                marker-end="url(#arwG)"></path>
            <rect
                x="444"
                y="26"
                width="140"
                height="46"
                rx="9"
                fill="#eef5ee"
                stroke="#2f5d3a"
                stroke-width="1.5"></rect>
            <text
                x="514"
                y="46"
                text-anchor="middle"
                font-size="12"
                font-weight="700"
                fill="#2f5d3a">succeeded ✓</text
            >
            <text x="514" y="62" text-anchor="middle" font-size="8.5" fill="#244a2e"
                >→ result link · terminal</text
            >
            <!-- to failed -->
            <path
                d="M 316 96 C 360 116, 400 128, 442 128"
                fill="none"
                stroke="#9a2417"
                marker-end="url(#arwR)"></path>
            <rect
                x="444"
                y="106"
                width="140"
                height="46"
                rx="9"
                fill="#f7ecea"
                stroke="#9a2417"
                stroke-width="1.5"></rect>
            <text
                x="514"
                y="126"
                text-anchor="middle"
                font-size="12"
                font-weight="700"
                fill="#9a2417">failed ✗</text
            >
            <text x="514" y="142" text-anchor="middle" font-size="8.5" fill="#7a2218"
                >→ error · terminal</text
            >
        </g>
    </svg>
    <figcaption>
        One envelope, four states. <code>done=true</code> resolves to exactly one of <strong
            >succeeded</strong
        > (a <code>response</code>) or <strong>failed</strong> (an <code>error</code>) — never both,
        never neither.<sup><a href="#s1">1</a></sup>
    </figcaption>
</figure>
